__________________________________________
                                           
                                            STARGATE_2GATES_PREFAB_FROM_SKILLOR
                                            __________________________________________


This is a Stargate Prefab with Teleport Function. You can go trouth all 2 Sides. The Gate is not Button Activated. Also the Gate is open all the Time. Have F@T Fun


Put the "stargate_2way.vmf" File into you Prefab Folder. I dont know where you have your Prefab Folder, mine is in the Location:
C:Program Files\Steam\steamapps\User Name\sourcesdk\bin\ep1\bin\prefabs


Put the 2 VTF and the 1 VMT Files into the brophis Folder, if you dont have, create one. Most on:
C:Program Files\Steam\steamapps\User Name\counter-strike source\cstrike\materials\brophis


I have build this Prefab without any Graphic Programms, only with the Valve Hammer Editor.

If you create a Map with this Prefab, plz put me in your Credits.


I hope you like it.

Our skillor

The HORIZONB Textures are from the Member "sman8472" special thx to him.
